For the classification tasks, we employ balanced random forest (BRF)51 classifiers to predict chronic kidney disease (CKD) using both the KORA metabolomics and multi-omics datasets. The classifiers are individually fitted using the observed and different imputed data of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
