MGH COVID dataset The MGH COVID study includes plasma proteins measured for patients at three timepoints: on day 0 (D0) for all patients on the day they were hospitalized for COVID, and on days 3 (D3) and 7 (D7) for patients still hospitalized then. We utilize proteomics data from D0 (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
